{"tid":1438651,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【請廣傳，文宣攻淺藍】社會運動無影響我地生活！無影響經濟！","createTime":"2019-08-09T23:04:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-10T07:49:42.000Z","uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"3f9893dc5456f674d3f71e7d63aa437215e07120","tid":1438651,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T23:04:23.000Z","msg":"林鄭而家打經濟牌，我地文宣組要做野！<br />\n<br />\n我地要話畀人知連串運動並無影響我地生活！<br />\n<br />\n（正如對家奶共賣港都口口聲聲話無影響我地生活一樣）<br />\n<br />\n大家唔好再有潔癖，盡情發揮創意，做文宣啦！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n小弟呢度拋豬引肉：<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/09/185004_49f1f9c80e6665caf001443abb1195bf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F09%2F185004_49f1f9c80e6665caf001443abb1195bf.png&h=deacb561&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"86ce360ffc13ff4eb0632d74965239083ba7abfe","tid":1438651,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T23:13:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67dc08d7d63293b94007d535ce3b659e8a4e0c01","tid":1438651,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T23:22:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13a48dcd10987598a8e1bd33eea8a31deb3de21e","tid":1438651,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T23:28:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d4c0a2dd08744458bb3a58b66591fa982592b19","tid":1438651,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T23:47:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed9a731f4353851ba5c9957db433f717a6777aef","tid":1438651,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T23:59:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" c